程序包 P2V

类 VRect

java.lang.Object
P2V.VObj
P2V.VRect
public class VRect extends VObj
VRect is a class that represents a rectangle visual object in the application. It extends the VObj abstract class and inherits its properties and methods.
作者:
Telsa

  • 字段详细资料

    • roundedCorner

      protected Variable[] roundedCorner
      The rounded corner radius of four corners. [0] for top-left, [1] for top-right, [2] for bottom-left, [3] for bottom-right

    • spin

      protected Variable spin
      The spin property represents the rotation angle of the VRect object. Note: The spin property is not available in most VObj classes.

  • 构造器详细资料

    • VRect

      public VRect()
      Constructs a new VRect object with default values. The position is set to (0, 0), width and height are set to 100, and other properties have default values.

    • VRect

      public VRect(float w, float h)
      Constructs a new VRect object with the specified width and height. The position is set to (0, 0), and other properties have default values.
      参数:
      w - The width of the rectangle.
      h - The height of the rectangle.

    • VRect

      public VRect(float x, float y, float w, float h)

      参数:
      x - The x-coordinate of the position.
      y - The y-coordinate of the position.
      w - The width of the rectangle.
      h - The height of the rectangle.

      h - The height of the rectangle.

    • VRect

      public VRect(float x, float y, float w, float h, int a, int r, int g, int b)
      Constructs a new VRect object with the specified position, width, height, and fill color.
      参数:
      x - The x-coordinate of the position.
      y - The y-coordinate of the position.
      w - The width of the rectangle.
      h - The height of the rectangle.
      a - The alpha of the rectangle fill.
      r - The red of the rectangle fill.
      g - The green of the rectangle fill.
      b - The blue of the rectangle fill.

  • 方法详细资料

    • setRoundedCorner

      public void setRoundedCorner(float tl, float tr, float bl, float br)
      Sets the rounded corner radius of the rectangle for each corner.
      参数:
      tl - The radius for the top-left corner.
      tr - The radius for the top-right corner.
      bl - The radius for the bottom-left corner.
      br - The radius for the bottom-right corner.

    • setRoundedCorner

      public void setRoundedCorner(float r)
      Sets the same rounded corner radius for all corners of the rectangle.
      参数:
      r - The radius for all corners.

    • getRoundedCorner

      public Variable getRoundedCorner(int index) throws Exception
      Gets the rounded corner radius for the specified corner of the rectangle.
      参数:
      index - The index of the corner (0 for top-left, 1 for top-right, 2 for bottom-left, 3 for bottom-right).
      返回:
      The rounded corner radius for the specified corner.
      抛出:
      Exception - If the index is not a valid corner index (0, 1, 2, or 3).

    • pullCorner

      public void pullCorner(int index, float x, float y) throws Exception
      Moves the specified corner of the rectangle to the specified position.
      参数:
      index - The index of the corner (0 for top-left, 1 for top-right, 2 for bottom-left, 3 for bottom-right).
      x - The x-coordinate of the new position.
      y - The y-coordinate of the new position.
      抛出:
      Exception - If the index is not a valid corner index (0, 1, 2, or 3).

    • pullCornerRelatively

      public void pullCornerRelatively(int index, float x, float y) throws Exception
      Moves the specified corner of the rectangle relative to its current position.
      参数:
      index - The index of the corner (0 for top-left, 1 for top-right, 2 for bottom-left, 3 for bottom-right).
      x - The amount to move the corner along the x-axis.
      y - The amount to move the corner along the y-axis.
      抛出:
      Exception - If the index is not a valid corner index (0, 1, 2, or 3).
